snippet.title: SNK HEROINES Tag Team Frenzy - Features Trailer (Nintendo Switch, PS4)
snippet.description:
Learn more @ https://SNKHeroines.com
Preorder @ https://store.nisamerica.com/preorders/snk-heroines

A brand new type of party fighting game arrives with SNK HEROINES Tag Team Frenzy, with a unique mix to the genre, with new features and a learning curve for fans of all skill levels!

Who will be the belle of the brawl? SNK's toughest female fighters are pitted against one another in a brand-new 2 vs 2 fighting game! With a streamlined control system and unique KO mechanic, this is a fighting game built for fans of all levels of experience. The perfect dream match starts here! Coming to Nintendo Switch and PlayStation 4 in September 7, 2018!
